# Neurex testing (Vitest)

Canonical coverage map: [docs/TESTING.md](../../docs/TESTING.md). Commands: [docs/SCRIPTS.md](../../docs/SCRIPTS.md).

## Layout

| Package | Config | Environment | Test root |
| ------- | ------ | ----------- | --------- |
| `@neurex/tokens` | `packages/tokens/vitest.config.ts` | node | `packages/tokens/test/` |
| `@neurex/ui` | `packages/ui/vitest.config.ts` | jsdom | `packages/ui/test/components/<Name>/` |
| `@neurex/registry` | `packages/registry/vitest.config.ts` | node | `packages/registry/test/` |
| `neurex` (cli) | `packages/cli/vitest.config.ts` | node | `packages/cli/test/commands/`, `test/core/` |

No root workspace `vitest.config.ts` — per-package configs for VS Code discovery (Vitest 4).

## UI tests

- `*.variants.test.ts` — CVA class output for primitives.
- `*.render.test.tsx` — DOM smoke, className merge, key a11y roles.
- **Blocks/templates** — block install smoke in `packages/cli/test/commands/install-flow.test.ts`; render smoke for FormField, Sidebar, DashboardShell in `@neurex/ui`; narrow viewport remains manual sandbox ([TESTING.md § Consumer sandbox verification](../../docs/TESTING.md#consumer-sandbox-verification)).

## Commands

```sh
pnpm check                    # full gate
pnpm tokens:check
pnpm ui:check                 # includes ui:audit
pnpm registry:check
pnpm --filter ./packages/cli check
```

Use **`$monorepo-check-gate`** skill to pick scoped checks by touched paths.

## Conventions

- Prefer behavior assertions over snapshots.
- Mock filesystem/network at CLI test boundaries; use temp dirs for install-flow tests.
- After UI variant changes, run `pnpm ui:audit` — token literals in `*.variants.ts` only.
